{
  "texts": [
    "For instance, T. Serizawa et al.",
    "analyzed multiple polymer species by peptide-based fluorescence sensing combined with linear discriminant analysis 48.",
    "The main limitation was its applicability only to uncommon water-soluble polymers in high concentrations (10 mg L -1).",
    "In contrast, the AgF@AgM@C10 can detect PS at ≈6000× lower concentration (0.0015 mg L -1).",
    "MPs found in the environment begin as components of plastic products that are increasingly pulverized into smaller pieces with irregular shapes."
  ]
}